CREATE TABLE [adventureworks_schema].[Date_Dim]
( 
	[DateID] [date]  NOT NULL,
	[Date] [date]  NOT NULL,
	[Day] NVARCHAR(10)  NOT NULL,
	[Month] NVARCHAR(10) NOT NULL,
	[Year] int  NOT NULL
)

(
	DISTRIBUTION = ROUND_ROBIN,
	CLUSTERED COLUMNSTORE INDEX
)
